source: crates/tokenless-cli/tests/e2e_tests.rs
expression: output
---
Delete specific records from stats

Usage: tokenless stats delete [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --id <ID>          Delete a single record by ID
      --secure-default   Enable stricter secure defaults for validation, logging, and helper execution
      --agent <AGENT>    Delete all records for a specific agent
      --before <BEFORE>  Delete all records before a date (ISO 8601, e.g. "2026-05-01")
      --yes              Skip confirmation prompt
  -h, --help             Print help
